      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE DEVIL ROLLS ON (4) went back last start and couldn't get into the race when 30 metres from the winner in sixth at this track over 1790m. Has failed to fire since she was in the placings at this track on February 11. This doesn't look as hard so she is in the right race to return to form. APOLOGY ACCEPTED (2) good effort to finish third two starts ago at this track but was less impressive at his latest appearance over 2190m at this track, beaten 65 metres into seventh after being close to the pace throughout. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Ideally placed and is sure to prove tough to beat. TAP TO PAY (5) ended last prep with a tenth at Swan Hill over 1750m 12 weeks ago. Can open this campaign with a more positive effort. INDIANAS SON (1) is in the mix following a fourth at his most recent appearance over 2190m at this track after arcing three-wide without cover at the bell.",
